---
title: Creamy Chicken Gnocchi with Tarragon and Tenderstem
description: Our chefs have been creating recipes for a while now and one thing they’ve learnt along the way is that creamy chicken and tarragon are a classic flavour combination our customers absolutely love. In this 15-minute recipe, we’ve combined creamy tarragon chicken with gnocchi and tenderstem broccoli for a warm and comforting recipe that really hits the spot.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-gnocchi-fc7c193c-da693b32.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/creamy-chicken-gnocchi-5c011f3ce3f3394a936adba2-1a72ee85.pdf
